  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience the Ultimate Bullet Hell Thrill with Fast-Paced 20-30 Minute Combats!</h2>Face swarms of monsters and bullet-hell chaos, enjoying the roguelike excitement and satisfying combat! Each game lasts 20-30 minutes, perfect for quick relaxation, stress relief, and pure catharsis.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812820/extras/a735c603d61760f5eebf6ee6b5170e4d.poster.avif?t=1772622113\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812820/extras/a735c603d61760f5eebf6ee6b5170e4d.webm?t=1772622113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812820/extras/a735c603d61760f5eebf6ee6b5170e4d.mp4?t=1772622113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Match Your Character and Weapons for Endless Possibilities</h2>With 10 characters and 7 weapons to choose, you can create your unique playstyle. Whether you want to master a single genre or become a magical swordsman with both magic and swordplay, it all depends on you!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812820/extras/9b457d58bb9151a71c706fed70d94988.poster.avif?t=1772622113\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812820/extras/9b457d58bb9151a71c706fed70d94988.webm?t=1772622113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812820/extras/9b457d58bb9151a71c706fed70d94988.mp4?t=1772622113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover Multiple Build and Hidden Talents</h2>Each build offers a complete progression path:<br>Gun Mastery → Cannon → Gunner Training<br>Hero Training → Magic Swordsman Training → Crystal Sword → Elemental Crystal Sword<br>Each path also includes different branches and directions to explore.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812820/extras/d4b5988fe9d0abf7795c82602d6d5d50.poster.avif?t=1772622113\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812820/extras/d4b5988fe9d0abf7795c82602d6d5d50.webm?t=1772622113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812820/extras/d4b5988fe9d0abf7795c82602d6d5d50.mp4?t=1772622113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adjustable Difficulty and Unique Monster Design</h2>Every level allows players to freely adjust the difficulty. <br>Unique and interesting monster designs enrich the combat experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812820/extras/71527221b509971adba1a0f63aa54c66.poster.avif?t=1772622113\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812820/extras/71527221b509971adba1a0f63aa54c66.webm?t=1772622113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812820/extras/71527221b509971adba1a0f63aa54c66.mp4?t=1772622113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Discord: ",
