nnon → Gunner Training<br>Hero Training → Magic Swordsman Training → Crystal Sword → Elemental Crystal Sword<br>Each path also includes different branches and directions to explore.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812820/extras/d4b5988fe9d0abf7795c82602d6d5d50.poster.avif?t=1772622113\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812820/extras/d4b5988fe9d0abf7795c82602d6d5d50.webm?t=1772622113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812820/extras/d4b5988fe9d0abf7795c82602d6d5d50.mp4?t=1772622113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adjustable Difficulty and Unique Monster Design</h2>Every level allows players to freely adjust the difficulty. <br>Unique and interesting monster designs enrich the combat experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812820/extras/71527221b509971adba1a0f63aa54c66.poster.avif?t=1772622113\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812820/extras/71527221b509971adba1a0f63aa54c66.webm?t=1772622113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812820/extras/71527221b509971adba1a0f63aa54c66.mp4?t=1772622113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Discord: ",
